MVCView - Interface in com.example.moodmasters.MVC
Class that represents the view part of the MVC framework, all UI classes will extend this interface if there exists a UI element in that class that can be interacted with that brings up a different activity or fragment, or initiates some sort of data manipulation in the backend.
